Package: e2p
Type: Package
Title: Effect-to-Prediction (E2P)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Povilas", "Karvelis", email = "karvelis.povilas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimates real-world predictive utility from empirical data
    distributions. Computes effect sizes, discrimination metrics, and
    threshold-dependent classification metrics with bootstrap confidence
    intervals. Includes support for binary (two-group) and continuous
    (predictor-outcome) analyses, as well as reliability deattenuation
    transformations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    stats,
    graphics,
    grDevices
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
